            .cases-bottom           
              .cases-content
                h2.cases-title Secure Total Protection with Cloud Storage 
                .cases-about Acronis Backup offers complete protection by extending data security to the cloud. Through its own secure cloud data centers, Acronis Storage supports storage-level encryption and data replication, and is compliant with the European Union’s (EU) General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR), ISO 27-001 and HIPAA. In addition, it employs a new file-to-cloud storage format, which delivers heightened security and better protection from brute-force attacks.
