            .restore-slider
              .restore-items.js-restore-slider
                  .swiper-container
                    .swiper-wrapper
                      .restore-item.swiper-slide
                        .restore-title 21 Platforms Protected
                        .restore-caption Ensure recovery by securing all systems and consolidating all workloads. Acronis protects 21 platforms – physical, virtual or cloud. New applications can be integrated seamlessly into existing environments for continuous, complete data protection.
                      .restore-item.swiper-slide
                        .restore-title Acronis Instant Restore 
                        .restore-caption Reduce recovery times and immediately start a Windows or Linux virtual machine directly from storage. Acronis Instant Restore enables your backup VM to start running in seconds, while it invisibly moves your data to the host in the background.
                      .restore-item.swiper-slide
                        .restore-title Acronis Universal Restore 
                        .restore-caption Restore an entire system image to new, dissimilar hardware.  Acronis Universal Restore overcomes compatibility issues by analyzing the target system and injecting the drivers required to successfully boot the system. 
                      .restore-item.swiper-slide
                        .restore-title Acronis vmFlashback 
                        .restore-caption Resume business after a failure up to 100 times faster with rapid VMware vSphere VM recovery. VMware’s Changed Block Tracking (CBT) technology tracks and saves only the changed blocks of information in a VM backup.
